Module io.winterframework.mod.http.base
Package io.winterframework.mod.http.base

Interface Parameter

All Known Subinterfaces:
CookieParameter
public interface Parameter

Base parameter interface defining common HTTP parameter (eg. header, cookie, query parameter...).

Since:
1.0
Author:
Jeremy Kuhn
